glcm 0.3
========

* Reformat tests for `testthat` >= 0.8.

* Fix handling of window sizes other than 3 x 3.

* Rename test image to end in 3x3 (as it was run with a 3x3 window size).

* Add another test image with textures run with a 7x11 window size (to enable 
  further test cases).

* Update website address.

* Various fixes to docs.

glcm 0.2
========

*  Require Rcpp >= 0.11.0 (as Makevars and Makevars.win are no longer included 
   in package).

*  Minor fixes to docs.

glcm 0.1
========

*  Initial release to CRAN.
